Projects

(HTML,CSS,JavaScript) {/*project2*/} Recipe App Save your favorite recipes with this user friendly recipes app! Create, delete, and edit multiple recipes.

(HTML,CSS,JavaScript,React) {/*project3*/} Family Cards Fetches weather data from OpenWeather API and keeps track of my family member location, weather, and time.

(HTML,CSS,JavaScript,React) {/*project3*/} Hockey Shop Oniline ice hockey retail shop. Able to add and remove items from the cart, and also 'checkout' at the end.
